<item>
            <title>[LU-19820] O2IB build failure with recent ofa_kernel packages</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19820</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Starting with recent DOCA packaging, for some of them,&lt;br/&gt;
the kernel include directory for ofa_kernel is now a symlink,&lt;br/&gt;
which is causing a `find` command to fail.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Add -H to ensure find follow that path if this is a symlink.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
